text: (light music)
- Hi, I'm Tiffanny Johnson,

and welcome to "Startup
with AWS Startups,"

where we bring you the
latest news and updates
from the AWS Startups universe.

So, let's kick it off
with Startup Day Miami.
This event is happening April 4th
to kick off Miami's Tech Month

with our free can't miss event
for the startup ecosystem.

Startup Day Miami will
feature an all-star lineup
of breakout sessions, technical workshops,
panels, partner demos, and more.
Be sure to register at the link below,
and we'll see you in Miami.
In other exciting news,

the AWS Impact Accelerator
Women Founders Program
wrapped up with all 25 participants
pitching their startups

to a packed room of
investors, mentors, and more.
We wish all the amazing participants luck,
and we'll be keeping an eye on your wins.

Have you visited an AWS
Startup loft lately?
Well, you should.
Because we have exciting upcoming program

at both the San Francisco
and New York locations,
including "Continue Evolving your MVP
"and Exceed User Expectations" workshop.
Click the link below to register
for a variety of workshops
that fit your startup needs.
Now let's turn to our read of the week.
Are you into digital disruptors?

Well, look no further than
our startups blog on Ava Labs,

the startup that's fueling
the mainstream growth
and innovation of blockchain.
Give it a read and share your thoughts.

Finally, we're going to
leave you with a peek

into our Startups in
the Stadium at re:Invent
celebration of the startup community
that we're all still recovering from.
(upbeat music)

Learn more about all events and
programs at the links below.
Thanks for watching,

and don't hesitate to
start up in the AWS Cloud.
